@clubId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@bookingId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### List bookings — next 7 days, all clubs, all types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — only open games (matchmaking front door)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings?type=Game&open=true
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — only full games
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings?type=Game&open=false
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — filtered by club
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings?clubId={{clubId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### List bookings — explicit time window
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings?clubId={{clubId}}&fromUtc=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&toUtc=2026-05-08T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Create booking — Game, open (any authenticated user)
# @name createBooking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "clubId": "{{clubId}}",
  "type": "Game",
  "slots": [
    "2026-05-01T18:00:00-04:00",
    "2026-05-01T18:30:00-04:00"
  ],
  "isPrivate": false,
  "description": null
}

### Create booking — Game, private (only participants can see it)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "clubId": "{{clubId}}",
  "type": "Game",
  "slots": [
    "2026-05-01T18:00:00-04:00",
    "2026-05-01T18:30:00-04:00"
  ],
  "isPrivate": true,
  "description": "Private match — invite only"
}

### Create booking — DayUse (club staff, owner, or admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "clubId": "{{clubId}}",
  "type": "DayUse",
  "slots": [
    "2026-05-01T10:00:00-03:00",
    "2026-05-01T11:00:00-03:00",
    "2026-05-01T12:00:00-03:00",
    "2026-05-01T13:00:00-03:00"
  ],
  "courtsToOccupy": 1,
  "capacity": 16,
  "isPrivate": false,
  "description": "Open day at the club — all members welcome"
}

### Join Booking — uses id from Create Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings/{{createBooking.response.body.bookingId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Join Booking (manual id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings/{{bookingId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Delete Booking (ClubStaffOrAdmin) — cascades to reservations + participants
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv TOKEN}}
